16. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. We will tell you about any changes by posting an updated policy on our site and (where appropriate) notifying you by post or email. Any such modification will be effective immediately upon posting on the site.  Where applicable law requires us to do so, we will seek your consent for such changes and give you an opportunity to cancel your subscription.
